abstract: Live coverage and analysis of the Giants' Week 17 showdown against the Dallas Cowboys at MetLife Stadium.
lead_paragraph: The Giants claimed the N.F.L.'s last playoff spot in convincing fashion Sunday night, overpowering the Dallas Cowboys, 31-14, at MetLife Stadium to win the N.F.C. East.
